end</span>
<span class="text-[#22d3ee]">```</span>

<span class="text-[#94a3b8]">## 5. Features & Requirements</span>

<span class="text-[#fbbf24]">### 5.1 User Management (Admin)</span>

#### 5.1.1 List Users
- Display all users in a table
- Show: name, email, admin status, created date
- Pagination

#### 5.1.2 Create User
- Admin can create a user with: email, name, password
- Generates API token automatically

